Inclusion Criteria:

1. Psoriatic arthritis meeting CASPAR criteria;
2. Active psoriatic arthritis defined by at least 1 swollen joint;
3. cDAPSA score ≥ 10; See also Exclusion #4 - cDAPSA must be \> 14 in patients without psoriasis.
